# Optional Google Drive integration. Both values are OPTIONAL.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in whichever you have. The app works without
# either: you can always drag/drop a local file or paste a public Drive link.
#
# - VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID: enables the "Browse Google Drive" button (OAuth + Picker).
#   When unset, the Browse button simply does not appear.
# - VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY: lets the app fetch *public* Drive files from a pasted link,
#   and is also required by the Picker. When unset, pasted links rely on the file
#   being publicly fetchable (often blocked by CORS) — drag/drop still works.
#
# See README.md ("Google Drive setup") for how to create these in Google Cloud.

VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY=
